item.title:
Mandy Moore & Kumail Nanjiani to star in ‘THREAD: AN INSIDIOUS TALE,’ a new film in the Insidious universe.
It follows husband and wife who enlist the help of a spell to travel back in time, so they can prevent the death of their young daughter.
